reviewText: Well, after having it for a few months, I finally finished watching it--and I MUST rewatch it!!  It's definitely NOT a kid's movie....but it's good for someone who doesn't mind getting a little creeped out!  You can't just watch it once.
Great movie for a gift.  Came in great time.
it's alright alright.. Its their second movie they made. Still great job! ;-)
